What is bachstats?
------------------

A simple tool to help on creating a dashboard to play with indicators and trends. A simple way to build reports and review your daily data. 


How to run the code?
--------------------

Download play:
http://www.playframework.org/

Add play to your path, to make easy calls using just "play":
export PATH=$PATH:/current/path/to/lib/play-1.2.3

If you want to integrate this app to Eclipse IDE, call this command:
play eclipsify bachstats
If you call integration to another IDE, remember to add specific files generated into .gitignore file. 

Need a demo? Check Heroku:
--------------------------

http://bachstats.herokuapp.com/

